{"tid":2233343,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"高級助理刑事檢控專員周天行去信陳志全 考慮介入私人檢控郭偉強案","createTime":"2020-10-07T05:14:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T05:31:20.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"67d77c3623361a2664a147323f312fe77392b1bc","tid":2233343,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T05:14:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkt1-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/120770717_3470923232954179_3345527483888698158_n.jpg?_nc_cat=106&amp;_nc_sid=dbeb18&amp;_nc_ohc=eVvEtyQlC78AX97oEM3&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkt1-2.xx&amp;oh=185d8eb3e4ed98e6861dbb990701bfaf&amp;oe=5FA3B5B1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkt1-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F120770717_3470923232954179_3345527483888698158_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D106%26_nc_sid%3Ddbeb18%26_nc_ohc%3DeVvEtyQlC78AX97oEM3%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkt1-2.xx%26oh%3D185d8eb3e4ed98e6861dbb990701bfaf%26oe%3D5FA3B5B1&h=6190d652&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n私人檢控郭偉強案 陳志全接律政司通知正考慮是否介入<br />\n<br />\n人民力量陳志全早前向工聯會郭偉強提出私人檢控，陳志全接獲律政司通知，正考慮是否介入案件。陳志全星期一收到律政司的信件，指正考慮是否介入案件，若陳志全有額外文件，要在本月19日或之前提供，律政司會基於現有文件及資料考慮並作決定。陳志全表示，會向律政司提供文件。有關案件涉及陳志全在5月的立法會內務委員會選主席期間，懷疑被郭偉強拉倒地上。案件上月在西九龍裁判法院提堂，律政司代表在庭上表示，律政司對是否介入未有立場，仍要6星期考慮相關證據，希望押後案件，但主任裁判官羅德泉表示，律政司沒有詳細交代考慮進度，加上律政司隨時可以介入，決定按常規處理案件。案件將於11月9日審前覆核。<br />\n<br />\n2020-10-07 11:15:37<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/rthk_new_c/135401\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frthk_new_c%2F135401&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmfsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=60b732fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/rthk_new_c/135401</a>"},{"pid":"3b5977c113fdf837b43bee5b44d08be4c144579e","tid":2233343,"uid":78892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T05:14:56.000Z","msg":"又嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bdbe8f4de7481711c2c850837c0c28d22d837d8","tid":2233343,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b5977